description:
Crestridge Ecological reserve is a relatively new park area.There are a number of trails in the area used by hikers, mountain bikers and equestrians. It's relatively easy hike with some scenic views in places. 
There is more than one starting location. For a hike close to San Diego this one had very few people.
http://www.earthdiscovery.org/crestridge-ecological-reserve
directions:
In El Cajon.
From I 8, south on Greenfield, left on La Cresta, left on Mountain View  and left on Horsemill Rd. Address closest to parking 1171 Horsemill Rd
title: Crestridge Ecological Reserve
